data.description: Welcome to Chandler Downs and this 1-level, 4-sided brick beauty! The perfect split floor plan features 3 bedrooms, 2 and 1/2 bathrooms plus an office/bonus room which could be used as an extra bedroom, a large kitchen with plenty of cabinet and counter space, a spacious living room with vaulted ceilings, a separate dining room and a lovely owners suite complete with a walk-in closet, dual vanities, separate shower and garden tub. This one includes all of the appliances, even the washer and dryer! Step out the back door to enjoy the large screened porch overlooking a beautiful level lot. Call to schedule your private showing today!
